Package poised

package poised
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Architect
    Subclass to create an Architect object with information about the person responsible for designing the building project for Poised.
    Customer
    Subclass to create an Customer object with information about the person for which the Poise building project is being designed and constructed for.
    EditAndFinaliseProject
    Subclass that edits and sets new information attributed to a Project object from the projectList selected by the user.
    Engineer
    Subclass to create an Architect object with information about the person responsible for designing the building project for Poised.
    Main
    The main code for the Poised Project Management System that displays various program menu options and executes operations according to the user's input.
    Manager
    Subclass to create a Manager object with information about the person responsible for managing the building projects for Poised.
    Person
    Parent class that captures and edits the information of people set as attributes of the Project object.
    Project
    Parent class that captures and edits the information to create an instance of a Project.
    ReadAndWriteToDatabase
    Abstract class that reads and writes project object information to and from a database.
    SearchAndViewProjects
    Abstract class that allows a user to search and view the details of a Project object, as well as view all projects, view overdue projects and view incomplete projects retrieved from the list of projects.
